name: "The Deviant Queen of the Shattered Blocks": AI 4K Limited Edition
description: The Russian backyard girl of the '90s... All the boys wanted her attention, but she was unattainable for those who did not have the attributes of that time: Levi's jeans, Adidas sneakers and Turbo bubble gum... It was only time that put everything in its place: the boys grew up and the queens grew old. Keep the memories of the past. (Model: @aspiratova)
